      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(approvals): handle stale plugin waits",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Extend the shared approval-not-found classifier to cover the gateway waitDecision stale-id message `approval expired or not found`.\n- Reuse that classifier in plugin approval waits for before_tool_call, Codex app-server approvals, native hook relay PermissionRequest approvals, and the existing exec approval wait path.\n- Preserve fail-closed behavior for stale plugin approval waits while leaving unrelated gateway errors exceptional or on their existing unavailable path.\n\nCloses #88111.\n\n## Validation\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/infra/approval-errors.test.ts src/agents/agent-tools.before-tool-call.e2e.test.ts extensions/codex/src/app-server/approval-bridge.test.ts src/agents/harness/native-hook-relay.approval-wait.test.ts` -> 4 Vitest shards passed; 4 files / 97 tests passed.\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/bash-tools.exec-approval-request.test.ts src/agents/harness/native-hook-relay.test.ts src/agents/harness/native-hook-relay.approval-wait.test.ts src/infra/approval-errors.test.ts` -> 2 Vitest shards passed; 4 files / 96 tests passed.\n- `node --import tsx --input-type=module ...real gateway stale plugin waitDecision proof...` -> passed; real gateway/client error `approval expired or not found`, `isApprovalNotFoundError=true`.\n- `env OPENCLAW_CHECK_CHANGED_REMOTE_CHILD=1 OPENCLAW_CHANGED_LANES_RAW_SYNC=1 CI=1 PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false corepack pnpm check:changed --base upstream/main` -> passed.\n- `git diff --check` -> passed.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n- **Behavior addressed:** Stale or missing `plugin.approval.waitDecision` approval ids now fail closed as typed stale/unavailable/deferred approval outcomes instead of surfacing as generic runtime/tool failures.\n- **Real environment tested:** Local OpenClaw source checkout on macOS with Node 24.15.0 and current PR head `f78c8ae5c7f3eb2783f84c252fd1ca31e4db3828`; started a real loopback OpenClaw gateway process from this checkout with an isolated temporary config/state dir and real token auth.\n- **Exact steps or command run after this patch:** Started a real gateway with `createOpenClawTestInstance(...).startGateway()`, connected a real gateway client with `operator.approvals` scope, then called the actual gateway/client request path through `client.request(\"plugin.approval.waitDecision\", { id: \"plugin:proof-stale-id\" }, { timeoutMs: 5000 })` against an intentionally stale/missing plugin approval id. After catching the live gateway error, checked it with the patched shared `isApprovalNotFoundError` classifier. Also ran the focused approval harnesses and the changed-file type/lint/import-cycle gate.\n- **Evidence after fix:** Redacted terminal output from the after-fix real-gateway run:\n```text\n$ node --import tsx --input-type=module - <<'SCRIPT'\n...starts createOpenClawTestInstance gateway and calls plugin.approval.waitDecision with plugin:proof-stale-id...\nSCRIPT\n[proof] real gateway started on loopback test port\n[proof] connected gateway client with operator.approvals scope\n[proof] call: plugin.approval.waitDecision id=plugin:proof-stale-id\n[proof] gateway/client error: approval expired or not found\n[proof] isApprovalNotFoundError=true\n[proof] result: stale plugin approval id is recognized by patched approval-not-found classifier\n[proof] cleanup: stopped gateway and removed temporary test state\n```\nAdditional focused harness output:\n```text\n$ node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/infra/approval-errors.test.ts src/agents/agent-tools.before-tool-call.e2e.test.ts extensions/codex/src/app-server/approval-bridge.test.ts src/agents/harness/native-hook-relay.approval-wait.test.ts\n[test] passed 4 Vitest shards in 16.70s\n\n$ node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/bash-tools.exec-approval-request.test.ts src/agents/harness/native-hook-relay.test.ts src/agents/harness/native-hook-relay.approval-wait.test.ts src/infra/approval-errors.test.ts\n[test] passed 2 Vitest shards in 6.38s\n\n$ env OPENCLAW_CHECK_CHANGED_REMOTE_CHILD=1 OPENCLAW_CHANGED_LANES_RAW_SYNC=1 CI=1 PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false corepack pnpm check:changed --base upstream/main\n[check:changed] lanes=core, coreTests, extensions, extensionTests\n[check:changed] typecheck core\n[check:changed] typecheck core tests\n[check:changed] typecheck extensions\n[check:changed] typecheck extension tests\n[check:changed] lint core\n[check:changed] lint extensions\n[check:changed] runtime import cycles\nImport cycle check: 0 runtime value cycle(s).\n```\n- **Observed result after fix:** The real gateway/client stale-id path produced `approval expired or not found`, and the patched shared classifier returned `true` for that live error. The patched before_tool_call path returns `Plugin approval unavailable (stale approval)` and blocks even when `timeoutBehavior` is `allow`; Codex app-server returns `{ decision: \"decline\" }` and emits an `unavailable` approval event; native hook relay PermissionRequest returns a no-op/defer response instead of throwing.\n- **What was not tested:** I did not run a browser approval UI or manually restart a long-lived production gateway mid-approval; the real proof uses an isolated local gateway process and a real gateway/client stale approval id response, with the sibling app-server/native/before_tool_call mappings covered by focused source-path tests.\n\n## Attribution\nIf this PR is squash-merged or reworked, please preserve commit author attribution for Andy Ye <35905412+TurboTheTurtle@users.noreply.github.com> or include `Co-authored-by: Andy Ye <35905412+TurboTheTurtle@users.noreply.github.com>`.\n",
